Career opportunity at Synesis IT Ltd.
Synesis IT,Top ranked IT firm in Bangladesh is looking for Sr. Programmer/ Programmer in their Software Development Team.
Post: Sr. Programmer/ Programmer
Job Requirements:
ÔÇ∑ Educational Requirements: B.Sc / M.Sc in CSE from reputed university.
ÔÇ∑ Total Experience: 1 - 04 Years;
ÔÇ∑ At least 02 Years of experience in Java Spring Boot, Spring MVC, Spring Data JPA, Spring Security,
ORM, Maven Build tools, Thymeleaf, Junit;
ÔÇ∑ Strong Knowledge of OOP, OOAD, SOA, Dependency Injection or IOC, REST API, Design Pattern;
ÔÇ∑ Strong knowledge of RDBMS, practical experience in Oracle PLSQL is preferred;
ÔÇ∑ Knowledge of Javascript, JQuery, CSS, Angular, TypeScript;
ÔÇ∑ Hands on Experience on BPMN, UML Diagrams (Use Case, Activity, Sequence, State);
ÔÇ∑ Strong Capability of communication both written and verbal;
ÔÇ∑ Capable of handling problem solving and highly requirement of strong analytical skill;
ÔÇ∑ Must be capable of work under pressure and also be a Team Player;
ÔÇ∑ Practical work Experience in Linux Environment;
ÔÇ∑ Having practice of Git;
ÔÇ∑ Must have practice of writing unit testing tools;
N.B.: If you are capable to meet the above criteria then please apply.
.Job Location: Kawran Bazar, Dhaka.
Salary Range: Negotiable
If you are interested please send your updated CV with photographs to hr@synesisit.com.bd within Sep 30, 2019.

